contentfulProduct.seoTitle: Australian Merino Wool Open Cardigan Sweater
contentfulProduct.seoDescription: This classic women's cardigan is made from luxurious 100% Australian merino wool. It features a smooth and soft texture with a flattering silhouette. A high-quality, comfy piece made for easy layering.
contentfulProduct.title: Australian Merino Wool Open Cardigan Sweater

content.value: This classic women's cardigan is made from luxurious 100% Australian merino wool. It features a smooth and soft texture with a flattering silhouette. A high-quality, comfy piece made for easy layering.
Merino wool is 100% biodegradable, renewable, wrinkle resistant, UV resistant, and naturally breathable
Material: 100% Extra-fine Australian merino wool; 19.5 micron yarn quality
Produced in BSCI (Business Social Compliance Initiative) certified factories which aims to improve working conditions throughout the supply chain.
Origin: Fujian, China
Model is 5'9" and wearing a size Medium
Hand wash only.  Cold wash inside out. Lay flat to dry. Cool iron, or dry clean.
